These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, spy
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, surfing
The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, chef
1. the chef is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the chef is on the right of the entrepreneur##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | fanta   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | crime   |
| Sport         | surfing | cycling |
| Job     | entrepreneur | chef    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: avocado, cabbage
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, rock-climbing
2 different pets are kept: dog, rat
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, tram
1. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | avocado     | cabbage |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | hiking  |
| Pet           | rat         | dog     |
| Transport     | motorbike   | tram    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur
House: palace, farmhouse
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
2. the farmhouse house is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | soy-milk     | hot-chocolate |
| Job         | entrepreneur | accountant    |
| House         | palace         | farmhouse        |
| Transport   | bike         | helicopter    |

