.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-12::.
City: hamburg, prague
The people have 2 different jobs:  architect, dressmaker
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, indie
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
2. the fan of funk is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the architect##1
4. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| City         | prague   | hamburg |
| Job           | architect | dressmaker    |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | indie         |
| Sport         | sailing   | weightlifting |

